title: How To Build a DIY Quarterpipe - Behind The Scenes - Yer Welcome
description:
The Yer Welcome crew takes you step-by-step through the build process for Decenzo's new quarterpipe. 

Featuring Dave Bachinsky, Pat Duffy, Sierra Fellers, Mark Appleyard, TJ Rogers, and Ryan Decenzo.
